com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Class LabelPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.LabelPart

  • public final class LabelPart
extends Object
    A description of part of a label, used by a LabelDefinition. Each part of a LabelDefinition is either the identifier of a PropertyType, or a string literal.

    1.0
